name: Coca Cola Delivery Neomorphism Prototype
description:
#StayHomeKit by Coca Cola

Classic, classic, no sugar, diet, no sugar, classic...


At the start of the 2020 pandemic I attempted to reimagine how people would "Share a Coke". As great as a simple reusable UI may be, a much bolder skeuomorphic-design inspired by a 1950's vending machine can lead to a much better human experience.


Here is the result of my exploration. Go ahead and go into the file.


If you'd like guided tutorial on my other community files, go ahead and check out my YouTube Channel (this file is tutorial-less unfortunately)
